gov.va.isaac.ie.exporter

Class Rf2Export

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.isaac.util.AbstractProgressReporter
      • gov.va.isaac.ie.exporter.Rf2Export
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Exporter, ProgressReporter, org.ihtsdo.otf.tcc.api.concept.ProcessUnfetchedConceptDataBI, org.ihtsdo.otf.tcc.api.ContinuationTrackerBI

    public class Rf2Export
extends AbstractProgressReporter
implements Exporter, org.ihtsdo.otf.tcc.api.concept.ProcessUnfetchedConceptDataBI
    Generates a Release Format 2 style release files for a specified set of concepts in the database. This class implements ProcessUnfetchedConceptDataBI and can be "run" using the terminology store method iterateConceptDataInParallel.
    See Also:
    IHTSDO Technical Implementation Guide - Release File Specifications

        releaseType - the ReleaseType representing the type of release
        language - the LanguageCode representing the language of the release
        country - the COUNTRY_CODE representing the country associated with the release
        namespace - the String representing the namespace associated with the released content
        effectiveDate - specifying the official release date
        pathNid - the path nid
        viewCoordinate - specifying which versions of the concepts to include in this release. Should not include all status values.
        taxonomyParentNids - an integer representing the parent of taxonomy to release
